      • animateZoom

        public void animateZoom(Complex startPosition,
               Complex endPosition)
        Animated zooming. This zooms into the set with animation. The animation is split into 15 frames, 30 milliseconds apart. So the estimated time for the zooming is 0.45 seconds.
        Parameters:
        startPosition - The Complex Number of the top left corner once it has zoomed in.
        endPosition - The Complex Number of the bottom right corner once it has zoomed in.
